Rating: 4
This recipe was great! They had Rosemary Olive Oil bread at the bakery so I used that instead of sourdough. Also followed the other reviewers advice and broiled the chops for 3 minutes on each side without the breadcrumbs, then added the breadcrumbs and broiled for 3 minutes. This was the first time I made lamb at home and it was absolutely fool-proof and delicious!

Rating: 3
This was a very tasty dish! Although I only marinated the chops for 3 hours versus the time frame the recipe called for, I was still impressed with the results. If mint sauce and lamb is not your thing, this is a great alternative.

