Rating: 4
This recipe was a big hit. I found it very easy to prepare. Heeding the warnings about the burnt breadcrumbs, I changed the broiling time to 3 minutes on each side, then topped with the breadcrumbs and finished broiling only 2 minutes. Let the chops rest a few minutes before serving. Yum!

